(1) Place the "metamaster" directory in the root of your project.
(2) Place "$MetaMaster" within the <head> tag of your Page.ss template.
(3) Run /dev/build?flush=all in SilverStripe.
(4) Enter your global meta description and keywords in the two new fields under the "Metadata" tab of your site root
	in the SilverStripe admin panel.
	
Please note:
	(a) A meta descriptions in child pages will override the global description for that page.
	(b) Additional meta keywords in child pages will be appended to the global keyword set.